# Security Vulnerability Ignore List
# Purpose: Document accepted vulnerabilities for dev dependencies
# Scope: Development-only dependencies with acceptable risk
#
# Each line is a vulnerability ID (GHSA-* or CVE-*) to ignore.
# Add comments above each ID explaining why it's acceptable.

# pip: Symlink handling in tar extraction (CVE-2025-8869)
# Risk: Dev environment only, no untrusted sources
# Mitigation: Use Python 3.11+ with PEP 706 support
